<subSubSection pageId="150" pageNumber="548" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="150.[2054,2646,1951,2377]" pageId="150" pageNumber="548">
Seems to be sister to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Allen &amp; Loveridge" baseAuthorityYear="1927" box="[2379,2498,2117,2142]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Myosorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="150" pageNumber="548" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="geata">M. geata</taxonomicName>
, although further sampling is needed to confirm this relationship. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
